26constexpr int ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::kMaxNumSpatialLayers;
27constexpr int ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::kMaxNumTemporalLayers;
28
29ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::ScalabilityStructureKeySvc(int num_spatial_layers,
30 int num_temporal_layers)
31 : num_spatial_layers_(num_spatial_layers),
32 num_temporal_layers_(num_temporal_layers),
33 active_decode_targets_(
34 (uint32_t{1} << (num_spatial_layers * num_temporal_layers)) - 1) {
35 // There is no point to use this structure without spatial scalability.
36 RTC_DCHECK_GT(num_spatial_layers, 1);
37 RTC_DCHECK_LE(num_spatial_layers, kMaxNumSpatialLayers);
38 RTC_DCHECK_LE(num_temporal_layers, kMaxNumTemporalLayers);
39}
40
41ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::~ScalabilityStructureKeySvc() = default;
42
43ScalableVideoController::StreamLayersConfig
44ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::StreamConfig() const {
45 StreamLayersConfig result;
46 result.num_spatial_layers = num_spatial_layers_;
47 result.num_temporal_layers = num_temporal_layers_;
48 result.scaling_factor_num[num_spatial_layers_ - 1] = 1;
49 result.scaling_factor_den[num_spatial_layers_ - 1] = 1;
50 for (int sid = num_spatial_layers_ - 1; sid > 0; --sid) {
51 result.scaling_factor_num[sid - 1] = 1;
52 result.scaling_factor_den[sid - 1] = 2 * result.scaling_factor_den[sid];
53 }
54 return result;
55}
56
57bool ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::TemporalLayerIsActive(int tid) const {
58 if (tid >= num_temporal_layers_) {
59 return false;
60 }
61 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
62 if (DecodeTargetIsActive(sid, tid)) {
63 return true;
64 }
65 }
66 return false;
67}
68
69DecodeTargetIndication ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::Dti(
70 int sid,
71 int tid,
72 const LayerFrameConfig& config) {
73 if (config.IsKeyframe() || config.Id() == kKey) {
74 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(config.TemporalId(), 0);
75 return sid < config.SpatialId() ? DecodeTargetIndication::kNotPresent
76 : DecodeTargetIndication::kSwitch;
77 }
78
79 if (sid != config.SpatialId() || tid < config.TemporalId()) {
80 return DecodeTargetIndication::kNotPresent;
81 }
82 if (tid == config.TemporalId() && tid > 0) {
83 return DecodeTargetIndication::kDiscardable;
84 }
85 return DecodeTargetIndication::kSwitch;
86}
87
88std::vector<ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig>
89ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::KeyframeConfig() {
90 std::vector<LayerFrameConfig> configs;
91 configs.reserve(num_spatial_layers_);
92 absl::optional<int> spatial_dependency_buffer_id;
93 spatial_id_is_enabled_.reset();
94 // Disallow temporal references cross T0 on higher temporal layers.
95 can_reference_t1_frame_for_spatial_id_.reset();
96 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
97 if (!DecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/0)) {
98 continue;
99 }
100 configs.emplace_back();
101 ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig& config = configs.back();
102 config.Id(kKey).S(sid).T(0);
103
104 if (spatial_dependency_buffer_id) {
105 config.Reference(*spatial_dependency_buffer_id);
106 } else {
107 config.Keyframe();
108 }
109 config.Update(BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/0));
110
111 spatial_id_is_enabled_.set(sid);
112 spatial_dependency_buffer_id = BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/0);
113 }
114 return configs;
115}
116
117std::vector<ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig>
118ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::T0Config() {
119 std::vector<LayerFrameConfig> configs;
120 configs.reserve(num_spatial_layers_);
121 // Disallow temporal references cross T0 on higher temporal layers.
122 can_reference_t1_frame_for_spatial_id_.reset();
123 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
124 if (!DecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/0)) {
125 spatial_id_is_enabled_.reset(sid);
126 continue;
127 }
128 configs.emplace_back();
129 configs.back().Id(kDeltaT0).S(sid).T(0).ReferenceAndUpdate(
130 BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/0));
131 }
132 return configs;
133}
134
135std::vector<ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig>
136ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::T1Config() {
137 std::vector<LayerFrameConfig> configs;
138 configs.reserve(num_spatial_layers_);
139 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
140 if (!DecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/1)) {
141 continue;
142 }
143 configs.emplace_back();
144 ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig& config = configs.back();
145 config.Id(kDeltaT1).S(sid).T(1).Reference(BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/0));
146 if (num_temporal_layers_ > 2) {
147 config.Update(BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/1));
148 }
149 }
150 return configs;
151}
152
153std::vector<ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig>
154ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::T2Config(FramePattern pattern) {
155 std::vector<LayerFrameConfig> configs;
156 configs.reserve(num_spatial_layers_);
157 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
158 if (!DecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/2)) {
159 continue;
160 }
161 configs.emplace_back();
162 ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig& config = configs.back();
163 config.Id(pattern).S(sid).T(2);
164 if (can_reference_t1_frame_for_spatial_id_[sid]) {
165 config.Reference(BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/1));
166 } else {
167 config.Reference(BufferIndex(sid, /*tid=*/0));
168 }
169 }
170 return configs;
171}
172
173ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::FramePattern
174ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::NextPattern(FramePattern last_pattern) const {
175 switch (last_pattern) {
176 case kNone:
177 return kKey;
178 case kDeltaT2B:
179 return kDeltaT0;
180 case kDeltaT2A:
181 if (TemporalLayerIsActive(1)) {
182 return kDeltaT1;
183 }
184 return kDeltaT0;
185 case kDeltaT1:
186 if (TemporalLayerIsActive(2)) {
187 return kDeltaT2B;
188 }
189 return kDeltaT0;
190 case kDeltaT0:
191 case kKey:
192 if (TemporalLayerIsActive(2)) {
193 return kDeltaT2A;
194 }
195 if (TemporalLayerIsActive(1)) {
196 return kDeltaT1;
197 }
198 return kDeltaT0;
199 }
200 RTC_NOTREACHED();
201 return kNone;
202}
203
204std::vector<ScalableVideoController::LayerFrameConfig>
205ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::NextFrameConfig(bool restart) {
206 if (active_decode_targets_.none()) {
207 last_pattern_ = kNone;
208 return {};
209 }
210
211 if (restart) {
212 last_pattern_ = kNone;
213 }
214
215 FramePattern current_pattern = NextPattern(last_pattern_);
216 switch (current_pattern) {
217 case kKey:
218 return KeyframeConfig();
219 case kDeltaT0:
220 return T0Config();
221 case kDeltaT1:
222 return T1Config();
223 case kDeltaT2A:
224 case kDeltaT2B:
225 return T2Config(current_pattern);
226 case kNone:
227 break;
228 }
229 RTC_NOTREACHED();
230 return {};
231}
232
233GenericFrameInfo ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::OnEncodeDone(
234 const LayerFrameConfig& config) {
235 // When encoder drops all frames for a temporal unit, it is better to reuse
236 // old temporal pattern rather than switch to next one, thus switch to next
237 // pattern defered here from the `NextFrameConfig`.
238 // In particular creating VP9 references rely on this behavior.
239 last_pattern_ = static_cast<FramePattern>(config.Id());
240 if (config.TemporalId() == 1) {
241 can_reference_t1_frame_for_spatial_id_.set(config.SpatialId());
242 }
243
244 GenericFrameInfo frame_info;
245 frame_info.spatial_id = config.SpatialId();
246 frame_info.temporal_id = config.TemporalId();
247 frame_info.encoder_buffers = config.Buffers();
248 frame_info.decode_target_indications.reserve(num_spatial_layers_ *
249 num_temporal_layers_);
250 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
251 for (int tid = 0; tid < num_temporal_layers_; ++tid) {
252 frame_info.decode_target_indications.push_back(Dti(sid, tid, config));
253 }
254 }
255 frame_info.part_of_chain.assign(num_spatial_layers_, false);
256 if (config.IsKeyframe() || config.Id() == kKey) {
257 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(config.TemporalId(), 0);
258 for (int sid = config.SpatialId(); sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
259 frame_info.part_of_chain[sid] = true;
260 }
261 } else if (config.TemporalId() == 0) {
262 frame_info.part_of_chain[config.SpatialId()] = true;
263 }
264 frame_info.active_decode_targets = active_decode_targets_;
265 return frame_info;
266}
267
268void ScalabilityStructureKeySvc::OnRatesUpdated(
269 const VideoBitrateAllocation& bitrates) {
270 for (int sid = 0; sid < num_spatial_layers_; ++sid) {
271 // Enable/disable spatial layers independetely.
272 bool active = bitrates.GetBitrate(sid, /*tid=*/0) > 0;
273 SetDecodeTargetIsActive(sid, /*tid=*/0, active);
274 if (!spatial_id_is_enabled_[sid] && active) {
275 // Key frame is required to reenable any spatial layer.
276 last_pattern_ = kNone;
277 }
278
279 for (int tid = 1; tid < num_temporal_layers_; ++tid) {
280 // To enable temporal layer, require bitrates for lower temporal layers.
281 active = active && bitrates.GetBitrate(sid, tid) > 0;
282 SetDecodeTargetIsActive(sid, tid, active);
283 }
284 }
285}

288
289FrameDependencyStructure ScalabilityStructureL2T1Key::DependencyStructure()
290 const {
291 FrameDependencyStructure structure;
292 structure.num_decode_targets = 2;
293 structure.num_chains = 2;
294 structure.decode_target_protected_by_chain = {0, 1};
295 structure.templates.resize(4);
296 structure.templates[0].S(0).Dtis("S-").ChainDiffs({2, 1}).FrameDiffs({2});
297 structure.templates[1].S(0).Dtis("SS").ChainDiffs({0, 0});
298 structure.templates[2].S(1).Dtis("-S").ChainDiffs({1, 2}).FrameDiffs({2});
299 structure.templates[3].S(1).Dtis("-S").ChainDiffs({1, 1}).FrameDiffs({1});
300 return structure;
301}

303ScalabilityStructureL2T2Key::~ScalabilityStructureL2T2Key() = default;
304
305FrameDependencyStructure ScalabilityStructureL2T2Key::DependencyStructure()
306 const {
307 FrameDependencyStructure structure;
308 structure.num_decode_targets = 4;
309 structure.num_chains = 2;
310 structure.decode_target_protected_by_chain = {0, 0, 1, 1};
311 structure.templates.resize(6);
312 auto& templates = structure.templates;
313 templates[0].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SSSS").ChainDiffs({0, 0});
314 templates[1].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SS--").ChainDiffs({4, 3}).FrameDiffs({4});
315 templates[2].S(0).T(1).Dtis("-D--").ChainDiffs({2, 1}).FrameDiffs({2});
316 templates[3].S(1).T(0).Dtis("--SS").ChainDiffs({1, 1}).FrameDiffs({1});
317 templates[4].S(1).T(0).Dtis("--SS").ChainDiffs({1, 4}).FrameDiffs({4});
318 templates[5].S(1).T(1).Dtis("---D").ChainDiffs({3, 2}).FrameDiffs({2});
319 return structure;
320}

324FrameDependencyStructure ScalabilityStructureL2T3Key::DependencyStructure()
325 const {
326 FrameDependencyStructure structure;
327 structure.num_decode_targets = 6;
328 structure.num_chains = 2;
329 structure.decode_target_protected_by_chain = {0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1};
330 auto& templates = structure.templates;
331 templates.resize(10);
332 templates[0].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SSSSSS").ChainDiffs({0, 0});
333 templates[1].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SSS---").ChainDiffs({8, 7}).FrameDiffs({8});
334 templates[2].S(0).T(1).Dtis("-DS---").ChainDiffs({4, 3}).FrameDiffs({4});
335 templates[3].S(0).T(2).Dtis("--D---").ChainDiffs({2, 1}).FrameDiffs({2});
336 templates[4].S(0).T(2).Dtis("--D---").ChainDiffs({6, 5}).FrameDiffs({2});
337 templates[5].S(1).T(0).Dtis("---SSS").ChainDiffs({1, 1}).FrameDiffs({1});
338 templates[6].S(1).T(0).Dtis("---SSS").ChainDiffs({1, 8}).FrameDiffs({8});
339 templates[7].S(1).T(1).Dtis("----DS").ChainDiffs({5, 4}).FrameDiffs({4});
340 templates[8].S(1).T(2).Dtis("-----D").ChainDiffs({3, 2}).FrameDiffs({2});
341 templates[9].S(1).T(2).Dtis("-----D").ChainDiffs({7, 6}).FrameDiffs({2});
342 return structure;
343}

345ScalabilityStructureL3T3Key::~ScalabilityStructureL3T3Key() = default;
346
347FrameDependencyStructure ScalabilityStructureL3T3Key::DependencyStructure()
348 const {
349 FrameDependencyStructure structure;
350 structure.num_decode_targets = 9;
351 structure.num_chains = 3;
352 structure.decode_target_protected_by_chain = {0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 2, 2, 2};
353 auto& t = structure.templates;
354 t.resize(15);
355 // Templates are shown in the order frames following them appear in the
356 // stream, but in `structure.templates` array templates are sorted by
357 // (`spatial_id`, `temporal_id`) since that is a dependency descriptor
358 // requirement. Indexes are written in hex for nicer alignment.
359 t[0x0].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SSSSSSSSS").ChainDiffs({0, 0, 0});
360 t[0x5].S(1).T(0).Dtis("---SSSSSS").ChainDiffs({1, 1, 1}).FrameDiffs({1});
361 t[0xA].S(2).T(0).Dtis("------SSS").ChainDiffs({2, 1, 1}).FrameDiffs({1});
362 t[0x3].S(0).T(2).Dtis("--D------").ChainDiffs({3, 2, 1}).FrameDiffs({3});
363 t[0x8].S(1).T(2).Dtis("-----D---").ChainDiffs({4, 3, 2}).FrameDiffs({3});
364 t[0xD].S(2).T(2).Dtis("--------D").ChainDiffs({5, 4, 3}).FrameDiffs({3});
365 t[0x2].S(0).T(1).Dtis("-DS------").ChainDiffs({6, 5, 4}).FrameDiffs({6});
366 t[0x7].S(1).T(1).Dtis("----DS---").ChainDiffs({7, 6, 5}).FrameDiffs({6});
367 t[0xC].S(2).T(1).Dtis("-------DS").ChainDiffs({8, 7, 6}).FrameDiffs({6});
368 t[0x4].S(0).T(2).Dtis("--D------").ChainDiffs({9, 8, 7}).FrameDiffs({3});
369 t[0x9].S(1).T(2).Dtis("-----D---").ChainDiffs({10, 9, 8}).FrameDiffs({3});
370 t[0xE].S(2).T(2).Dtis("--------D").ChainDiffs({11, 10, 9}).FrameDiffs({3});
371 t[0x1].S(0).T(0).Dtis("SSS------").ChainDiffs({12, 11, 10}).FrameDiffs({12});
372 t[0x6].S(1).T(0).Dtis("---SSS---").ChainDiffs({1, 12, 11}).FrameDiffs({12});
373 t[0xB].S(2).T(0).Dtis("------SSS").ChainDiffs({2, 1, 12}).FrameDiffs({12});
374 return structure;
375}
